cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.NI 

This paper is about detecting and classifying malware on mobile devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses machine learning techniques to classify malware based on behavior, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also uses social network analysis to increase the modularity within each malware family network aggregation, which could fall under social and information networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper deals with mobile devices, which could fall under networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
